thread.title_full: Redspot Car Rentals reviewed by VICKI

author: VICKI
title: VICKI
text:
As my car had been ordered through an agent who had me down for picking up the car from the international and not domestic airport 12ks away, you can imagine my dismay at such a mistake.
Anyway, Jason ably assist me with a car from his office at the domestic terminal. A relief.
All with the up most courtesy and friendliness.
Thank you.
